  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/6c5cbdc16f64a33ac51c6e4f8bd867dd.avif?t=1750082242\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br>A bite-sized, turn-based strategy game about building your civilization -<i> and watching it fall</i>. <br><br>Use Tribes to expand your civilization, create Cities, buy Advances, build Wonders and send Expeditions, while preparing for the devastation that random events will bring. Only with careful planning and a little luck will your empire stand the test of time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/7832c9cea25e07b1722d10c396fef770.poster.avif?t=1750082242\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/7832c9cea25e07b1722d10c396fef770.webm?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/7832c9cea25e07b1722d10c396fef770.mp4?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⬢ A standard game mode with randomly generated starting conditions for endless replayability<br>⬢ 15 Scenarios with unique rules and conditions<br>⬢ 17 destructive event types to survive<br>⬢ 50 upgrades to empower your civilization<br>⬢ 10 Wonders to bring glory to your empire<br>⬢ A complete, interactive tutorial to help you master the game<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/bb26ca49f154b25402042fbc740ae5ef.poster.avif?t=1750082242\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/bb26ca49f154b25402042fbc740ae5ef.webm?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/bb26ca49f154b25402042fbc740ae5ef.mp4?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A digital version of the popular print-and-play game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/5a498bb377a4deebd4a5dd549a68612e.poster.avif?t=1750082242\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/5a498bb377a4deebd4a5dd549a68612e.webm?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/5a498bb377a4deebd4a5dd549a68612e.mp4?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/f21c1f8a5b61790c15461231b4dda10b.webp?t=1750082242\" width=154 height=43 /></span><br>Join us on Discord!<br>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/6c5cbdc16f64a33ac51c6e4f8bd867dd.avif?t=1750082242\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br>A bite-sized, turn-based strategy game about building your civilization -<i> and watching it fall</i>. <br><br>Use Tribes to expand your civilization, create Cities, buy Advances, build Wonders and send Expeditions, while preparing for the devastation that random events will bring. Only with careful planning and a little luck will your empire stand the test of time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/7832c9cea25e07b1722d10c396fef770.poster.avif?t=1750082242\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/7832c9cea25e07b1722d10c396fef770.webm?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/7832c9cea25e07b1722d10c396fef770.mp4?t=1750082242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⬢ A standard game mode with randomly generated starting conditions for endless replayability<br>⬢ 15 Scenarios with unique rules and conditions<br>⬢ 17 destructive event types to survive<br>⬢ 50 upgrades to empower your civilization<br>⬢ 10 Wonders to bring glory to your empire<br>⬢ A complete, interactive tutorial to help you master the game<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/bb26ca49f154b25402042fbc740ae5ef.poster.avif?t=1750082242\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532240/extras/bb26ca49f154b25402042fbc740ae5ef.webm?t=1750